{"tid":914382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"范冰冰曬李晨兒時照為其慶生：人間值得 生日快樂","createTime":"2018-11-24T08:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T03:08:05.000Z","uid":82917,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"43b541545400c7e189c65f32f4dd7a7052f5b38e","tid":914382,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:23:35.000Z","msg":"新浪娛樂訊 11月24日是李晨的生日，范冰冰曬出男友的兒時照片為其慶生，「人間值得，生日快樂。」隨後，李晨也回復稱，「人間值得。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWJMPXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWJMPXi.png&h=b266cebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uv7mDQN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuv7mDQN.png&h=6960e433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，官方正式公佈了范冰冰案的處理結果。稅務部門向范冰冰依法發出巨額罰單。范冰冰所需補繳的稅款、滯納金以及罰款加在一起超過8億。隨後，范冰冰在微博發佈道歉信，稱對自己的所作所為深感愧疚，完全接受稅務機關依法作出的一系列處罰決定，將按照決定「盡全力克服一切困難，籌措資金、補繳稅款、繳納罰款。」<br />\n<br />\n10月5日，李晨微博發文，稱：「甭管多難，咱們一起渡過去。」疑似公開表態，會陪在女友范冰冰身邊支持她。據悉，日前也曾有網友曬出疑似李晨的朋友圈截圖，圖片顯示，他分享了題目為「加油！范冰冰」的文章，暗中力挺女友。"},{"pid":"9b0fd47d7173deaca935756998718d8d8a96a7dc","tid":914382,"uid":21432,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"以後無得再講： 「我就是豪門」喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0c29349a93793ee6adcbe05dcd72678279fad6","tid":914382,"uid":5591,"like":148,"dislike":0,"score":148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"交稅，一點都不能少"},{"pid":"18b16a7d8a7f6d29c4bfd0ce5e8d8fee94748e6b","tid":914382,"uid":82917,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"9b0fd47d7173deaca935756998718d8d8a96a7dc","tid":914382,"uid":21432,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"以後無得再講： 「我就是豪門」喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:28:57.0